STATE
OF
THE
PATIENT
PATIENTS
WITH
CYSTIC
FIBROSIS
HAVE
IMPAIRED
GLUCAGON
AND
INSULIN
RELEASE
WHICH
ALTERS
THEIR
FAT
METABOLISM
THE
